    "Fig. 1 Scientific understanding can be categorized into various levels based on the number of questions answered.",
    "An agent possessing the ability to answer all the questions posed by scientific communities, including those for which we do not yet have answers, indicates a higher level of (new) scientific understanding 1 3",
    "There is a need for guidelines to establish a standardized and reliable approach to testing which ensures accurate and consistent results.",
    "In developing a comprehensive and reliable test for AI agents, it is crucial to define the test scope and purpose, ensuring it is tailored to the agent and includes a variety of difficulty levels.",
